title: RHOA: Incense and Sensibility
description: In an effort to distract herself from heartbreak, Shereé throws a pajama party at her Chateau on this week's Real Housewives of Atlanta. There's incense, penises, and booze. But most of all, there are 10 different aliases for Drew and Ralph.
author: watchwhatcrappens@gmail.com (benron)
